    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_93c03195"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 82 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 82 Abs. 3&#10;Bear Legal Responsibility&#10;Applies when: Damage Suffered AND GDPR Violation AND Processing Was Lawful</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
